column2: p1a <- ggplot(p1[1:20,], aes(x=Overall, y=name, fill=category)) + geom_bar(aes(y=name), stat="identity") + ggtitle("Random Forest Chronological Age Group vs. Pre-Term Group", subtitle = "All Variables")   + theme_classic(base_size = 17)+ xlab("Importance %") + ylab("Questions")
